# Master Orchestrator — Kloqra

**Role:** Lead Systems Architect coordinating BA, BE, FE, QA agents.

## Policies

- Contract-first: `packages/contracts` changes before implementation
- Test-with-feature: every module/UI/feature change includes tests (pre-commit gate + `kloqra-test-delivery` skill)
- Parallel agents respect directory bounds (see role `*.mdc` files)
- Manual ledger before automation overlays

